15
00:00:47.292 --> 00:00:49.167
<i>He's using the Freeport
to smuggle arms.</i>

16
00:00:53.417 --> 00:00:55.874
{\an8} <i>If Fisk moves those guns
into Red Hook. they vanish.</i>

17
00:00:55.875 --> 00:00:57.541
<i>I have something to show you.</i>

18
00:01:00.542 --> 00:01:03.625
<i>They're hunting us.
Maybe it's time we started hunting them.</i>

19
00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:11.074
