assault and attempted murder.

438
00:26:23.875 --> 00:26:25.291
this court finds you guilty.

439
00:26:25.292 --> 00:26:27.624
For the entertainment of the masses.

440
00:26:27.625 --> 00:26:29.207
Sentencing will follow later.

441
00:26:29.208 --> 00:26:32.499
Until such time.
you will be remanded back to detention.

442
00:26:32.500 --> 00:26:34.124
